h%E1%BA%A1ch-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-h%E1%BA%ADu-quan-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91/poem-Vqow27pdQlBUwaSkG3-PNQ">Thiên Thai thạch lương hậu quan bộc bố - 天台石梁雨後觀瀑布</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-zQyjfkM-l-eVSsp11IFYtg">Nguỵ Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-L%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-h%E1%BB%AFu-v%C3%A3n-thi-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7/poem-P5Qj_wbaycEHW5lHsgbjJQ">Tịnh hữu vãn thi nhất thủ - 并有輓詩一首</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Ph%C3%A0n-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-tam-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-ph%C3%B3-H%C3%A1n-Trung-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-gV8W2jkzRYVUPWD3eyzNhQ">Tống Phàn nhị thập tam thị ngự phó Hán Trung phán quan - 送樊二十三侍御赴漢中判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/U-c%C6%B0-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-m%E1%BB%99/poem-PMcUkZPlC76I8ldmcodWdA">U cư đông mộ - 幽居冬暮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
